### Search API Tests

### Get search suggestions (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/search/suggestions?q=test
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search across all entities (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/search?q=test&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search with special characters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/search?q=test@example.com&limit=5&page=1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search with empty query (should return error)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/search?q=
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search without authentication (should return 401)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/search?q=test